title: On Time (feat. B Slade)
lyrics:
On time
Don't you worry, don't you fret
Has there ever been a time where God has failed you
Don't you worry, don't you fret
Just keep your head facin' towards the sky
When I was sinking, you lifted me

When I get lonely, He comforts me

He's always there when I need Him the most

Feel my soul with the Holy Soul
